nodes.name: L-leucine:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Leucine + H2O + NAD+ <=> 4-Methyl-2-oxopentanoate + Ammonia + NADH + H+

nodes.name: L-Isoleucine:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Isoleucine + H2O + Oxygen <=> (S)-3-Methyl-2-oxopentanoic acid + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: (S)-Methylmalonate semialdehyde:oxygen oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Methylmalonate + Hydrogen peroxide <=> (S)-Methylmalonate semialdehyde + Oxygen + H2O

nodes.name: (S)-Methylmalonate semialdehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: (S)-Methylmalonate semialdehyde + NAD+ + H2O <=> Methylmalonate + NADH + H+

nodes.name: 2-Methyl-3-oxopropanoate:NAD+ oxidoreductase (CoA-propanoylating)
nodes.rxn: 2-Methyl-3-oxopropanoate + CoA + NAD+ <=> Propanoyl-CoA + CO2 + NADH + H+

nodes.name: 4-methyl-2-oxopentanoate:ferredoxin oxidoreductase (decarboxylating
nodes.rxn: 4-Methyl-2-oxopentanoate + CoA + 2 Oxidized ferredoxin <=> 3-Methylbutanoyl-CoA + CO2 + 2 Reduced ferredoxin + H+

nodes.name: 3-methyl-2-oxobutanoate:ferredoxin oxidoreductase (decarboxylating
nodes.rxn: 3-Methyl-2-oxobutanoic acid + CoA + 2 Oxidized ferredoxin <=> 2-Methylpropanoyl-CoA + CO2 + 2 Reduced ferredoxin + H+

nodes.name: (S)-3-methyl-2-oxopentanoate:ferredoxin oxidoreductase (decarboxylating
nodes.rxn: (S)-3-Methyl-2-oxopentanoic acid + CoA + 2 Oxidized ferredoxin <=> (S)-2-Methylbutanoyl-CoA + CO2 + 2 Reduced ferredoxin + H+

nodes.name: L-valine:NAD+ oxidoreductase(deaminating)

nodes.name: Acetoacetate:CoA ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Acetoacetate + CoA <=> AMP + Diphosphate + Acetoacetyl-CoA
